column3: “Dogwalker is my go to" strain for all my medical needs & believe me I have a few & DW cures them all!! It's very pungent

column3: “So I'll be totally honest, I'm completely new to the recreational marijuana scene. But this has one quite the kick. I have a laundry list of problems like anxiety, tremors and whatnot. All gone. I don't think I've ever had a medicine be an all in one"

column3: “Great flavor, enjoyable high. I made a mad dash (ok, a slow stumble) to the area" and grabbed some Dogwalker OG out of my grin...”"

“Cure all strain right here. The macGyver of cannabis. She is so beautiful to smoke. instant happiness and relief. Pain is gone. stress is goon, hunger is here and creativity is running through the blood. wish this one was around more.”
“one of the first strains I ever smoked, always had a great time. calm high with good feelings, help me recover from hard day's and kill time on day's off, highly recommend.”
“Takes me to the moon”
“Definitely getting the diesel in this bud. Sometimes I get a sour fruit taste off of it but I think I'm just too high.”
“kills the pain and brings the mind to beautiful elevation of intricate understandings.”

“Incredible on every level. Great power,Flavor and Aroma!!! This strain relieves pain,anxiety,ptsd,insomnia.Increases appetite. I would be a return customer simply because of this killer strain!!! But this Lil neighborhood shop has many great qualities!!! Great selection of flowers,concentrates and medibles. Prices for any budget.... Check them out😨😨😨😨😨”
“Simply amazing. Hands down the best flower I have tried in my life.”
“smells like walking a dog through a garden”

“Way to go Mitchell! All I needed was a budget-buzz and I found a new favorite. Dogealker OG is super soft and with a lite sweet taste. Great grounder to complete small tasks. I can't wait for Penny Gram Monday and Tuesday" I know what my pick will be
column4: let's see what Kaleafa's pick will be.”"

column3: “best smooth head high and minor pain relief I've found yet.”
“Walked the dog....to the dispensary. it was a win win for both the dog and I.”
“Tingly and anxious. I needed to lay down I got so dizzy 😵.”

“Migraine pain comin on; nausea 3-4 when I medicated round 1730 or so. Takes bout 5-10 min to start working. Nausea gone. Not working as well for the pain (3) but did help. Head high kinda heavy; it was hard to work out today. Body high quite frankly not good enough. Smells & tastes like sweet @$$! How the (ahem) does that work. Not the best by far. Will not be getting this strain again. :-(”
“It was truly great!”
“love this stuff and all the crosses of her including the Scooby Snacks. Pigfarm Organics DWOG is amazing”
“Not my first Walk in the Dog park but perhaps the most pleasant to date. B <--= L8r.”
“love it at the pg!!! thanks to my new follower kindgoddess420!!”
“Took the Dawg for a walk. Wow! I'm impressed. After three hits, I'm cooked. That's the stuff.”
“Who-hoo!!  Wow! Uplifting, happy and hungry.  Very nice during the day.”

“Exceptional Strain! Pungent, Skunky,with a hint of lemon. When done right a top shelf strain  with a good combination of mental and physical effects. The examples I've seen have beenbetween 23-30% THC. Very potent stuff, a must try!”
“It is a very high energy and it tastes awesome. One hit wonder!”
“Clear headed stress relief. Would be a good strain to smoke if you still wanted to do something with your day but wanted a nice mood enhancement.”
“its my favorite best high ever it relaxes you”

“Bong hits: Easy to milk, The taste is spot on. Great taste:D 
Metal pipe: HOT, Very tasty.
In general its fluffy" grinds nice but the burn is the best
“Good stoney feeling. Forgot about the neck and back pains. Not dry, breaks down good for blunts. Smooth smoking in water piece.”
“Uplifting high. Nice green buds,”
“Perfect Indica medication.”

“I used this a lot during spring break, and it completely took away a really bad headache that regular pain meds wouldn't help. Takes a while to sink in, and once it does is really calming. Didn't feel locked to my chair but could have easily spent the evening in. Instead, I went for a longboarding trip around the boardwalk and it was amazing.
The only thing was that it smelled super weird.”
